message: Hi Bob, I'm selling a product that I think you'll find valuable. I'm offering it to you for $95.
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I am only willing to pay $85 for it.
Bob, I understand your position, but the product is worth a lot to me. How about we meet in the middle at $90?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I am still not able to go above $87 for this product.
